<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,286,467]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Pericarp with 1-layered mesocarp. Seed narrowly cylindrical to narrowly pyramidal; aril tubular without lobes or with two string-shaped straight lobes.</paragraph>
